quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  54,41,Mazima okulabula kwajjira abantu ba Firawo
  54,42,"Baalimbisa ebigambo byaffe byonna, olwo nno netubakwata enkwata ya Nantakubwa ku mukono, nannyini buyinza"
  54,43,Abakafiiri ba mmwe be balungi okusinga abo! oba (ekibayinula) mulina akalagaane ku butavunaanwa nga kawandiikibwa mu bitabo ebitukuvu ebyasooka
  54,44,Oba (ekibayinula lwakuba) bagamba nti ffe tuli bangi nga twegasse tusobola okwetaasa
  54,45,(Zibasanze) ekibiina (ekyo) kijja kuwangulwa era bakubeyo amabega (badduke)
  54,46,(Byonna bye baliko temuli) wabula olunaku lw’enkomerero ye ndagaano yaabwe era olunaku lw’enkomerero lwelusinga obukalubo n’obukaawu
  54,47,Mazima abonoonyi bali mu bubuze na bugwi bwa ddalu
  54,48,(Bandibadde bajjukira) olunaku lwe baliwalulwa ku byenyi byabwe mu muliro (nga bwe bagambibwa nti) mukombe ku bulumi bw’omuliro Sakara
  54,49,Mazima ffe buli kintu twakitonda mu ngeri nga bwe kisaana okuba
  54,50,(Ate mu kukola ebintu byonna) ekiragiro kyaffe tekiri okugyako kimu nga kiringa lutemya lwa liiso
  54,51,"Era ddala twazikiriza abafaanana nga mmwe, abaffe waliyo eyebuuliridde"
  54,52,Na buli kintu kyonna kye baakola kiri mu kitabo
  54,53,Era buli kitono n'ekinene kyawandiikibwa
  54,54,Mazima abatya Katonda balibeera mu jjana n’emigga (egiriba gikulukutira wansi waazo)
  54,55,Mu kifo ekya mazima ew’omufuzi nannyini buyinza